    "Nevertheless, it's not quite proper to berate the progress of LLMs and their contribution to knowledge.",
    "They will get better in the future, and they will probably be the way to pinpoint information hidden in the literature that otherwise would have been hidden forever.",
    "But we must not overestimate what these models are capable of.",
    "Following, we dive deeper inside the technical part of this technology, in the hope that some things will be more evident.A little communicated fact is that ''Machine Learning'' in IT terminology, is nothing more than data compression.",
    "This is not a new approach since several deep learning techniques can be viewed through the lens of data compression."
